title: Warlock Defense v1.6
description:
Welcome to Warlock Defense!

The eyes of the enemy are over your lands. You must defend it! They attack by land and air but you have at your disposal all defensive measures of your kingdom and you powerful spells to face them. 

You have to conjure your spells and release at the exact moment, but the control of magic is not easy! Domitate it and crush your enemy!

Features:

- 3 game modes, campaign, skirmish and survival. 
- 12 original maps. 
- 16 types of enemies 
- 24 towers 
- 4 upgradeable spells 
- HD textures 
- Great graphics and sounds 
- Original soundtrack

Requirements:

- 1.0 GHz or better
- 32 MB Hard Drive
- 512 MB RAM or better

WARNING:

The domain of magic is decisive for victory. Use it well and joy!
LANGUAGES: English, Spanish, French, Portuguese, Italian

What's New:

- Added a tutorial
- Upgraded pathfinding system
- Fixed some issues
- New logo
